<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, June 2 (Xinhua) -- British and Iraqi government
officials will hold talks in London Tuesday to discuss the plans
for Iraq selling oil for food and medicines, according to local
press reports.
</P>
<P>
A British Foreign Office spokesman was quoted as saying this
afternoon that an Iraqi Oil Ministry delegation, including
director generals of the Oil Ministry's finance and distribution
departments, are due to arrive in Britain Tuesday for the
