Last weekend, the fundamentalist Taliban militia captured the
northern stronghold of Mazar-i-Sharif once held by warlord
Dostum in Afghanistan.
</P>
<P>
He hoped that those responsible for creating this tension
would change their policies in the interests of peace so as to
help reduce the bloodshed and miseries of the Afghan Muslims.
</P>
<P>
Mohammadi said that Iran is determined to continue its
humanitarian assistance to Afghanistan and called on international
organizations and countries the world over to aid and abet peace
efforts in Afghanistan. 
