implementation of the "one country, two systems" principle will
provide a good example for Macao, where the local people will
continue to work for a more prosperous Macao.
</P>
<P>
Maduro's 6-member delegation arrived in Beijing last Saturday
at the invitation of the China Association of Judges (CAJ). During
their stay in Beijing, they held talks with CAJ leaders, and
visited the Hong Kong and Macao Affairs Office of the State
Council.  
