<HEADLINE> Thailand, Israel to Cooperate on Juridical Procedures </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, June 3 (Xinhua) -- Thailand and Israel will cooperate
on juridical procedures, according to a press release issued by
the Thai Government House.
</P>
<P>
