agreement on cooperation on juridical procedures between Thailand
and Israel was approved today by the Thai Cabinet at its weekly
meeting.
</P>
<P>
Thailand and Israel will sign the agreement when Thai Foreign
Minister Prachuab Chaiyasarn visits Israel this month.  
