bought by Marketon Investment Ltd. at 6.06 billion HK dollars (780
million US dollars), with bidding opened at 3.8 billion HK dollars
(490 million US dollars).
</P>
<P>
The third lot, situated at Cheung Fu Street, Cheung Sha in
Lantau, was bought by Asia Chance Investment Ltd. at 40 million HK
dollars (5.13 million US dollars), with bidding opened at 10
million HK dollars (1.28 million US dollars).
</P>
<P>
