Ministry of Finance Monday announced that it would soon issue this
year's first batch of sovereign bonds (government-guaranteed
bonds).
</P>
<P>
A spokesman for the ministry said the issue would occur in
Europe and the currency would be in Deutsche mark bonds.
</P>
